data.description: Step into your dream home in sunny South Venice! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers a harmonious fusion of comfort and versatility. It boasts a bonus room capable of effortlessly serving as a fourth bedroom or a dedicated home office, tailored to meet your distinct requirements. Upon entry, a warm and inviting living area extends its cordial welcome. The open-concept layout seamlessly interconnects the living room with the dining area and kitchen, forging an idyllic space for family gatherings and entertaining friends. Throughout the house, bamboo and tile floors lend an air of grace. The well-appointed kitchen showcases modern appliances, abundant storage, and a convenient breakfast bar, rendering it a perfect canvas for culinary artistry, whether you are an accomplished chef or a passionate enthusiast. The primary bedroom suite stands as a tranquil retreat, featuring an en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms are thoughtfully designed for the comfort of family members or guests. The bonus room, with its limitless potential for transformation into a fourth bedroom, beckons with endless possibilities. Stepping outside, you'll discover a verdant backyard where you can bask in the Florida sun or host delightful barbecue gatherings. Conveniently situated in the heart of South Venice, this residence provides easy access to beautiful beaches, top-rated schools, shopping, and dining. It harmoniously combines modern living with coastal charm, offering you the quintessential Florida lifestyle you've long sought. Make this versatile and inviting house your forever home, where you can forge unforgettable memories, relish sun-kissed days, and luxuriate in the comforts of your 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom haven, with the adaptability of a bonus room catering to your ever-evolving needs. Welcome home to South Venice!
